# ==========================================
# Massive Audio Assets (Highly Recommended)
# ==========================================
# GitHub has a 100MB file limit and repositories should stay lightweight.
# This ignores the music tracks inside assets, but keeps the folder.
assets/*.mp3
!assets/.gitkeep